text: Hi Gordon Sumit! To prevent collecting data from non-HubSpot forms that do not have a class or ID, you can include a hidden label and input field, change the CSS ID or class attribute in your external form provider, toggle the "Collect data from website forms" switch on/off, or use the "Collect data from website forms" option in the Non-HubSpot Forms menu.
